    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>This GamiPress Add-on adds a shortcode to show a link. The user is then awarded a specified achievement when the link is clicked. This shortcode is fully integrated with the GamiPress shortcode insert button.</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> You need to install the free <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/gamipress/\" title=\"GamiPress\" rel=\"ugc\">GamiPress plugin</a>&trade; (version 1.4 or higher) to use the GamiPress Community Add-on. The Plugin was tested up to GamiPress 1.9.1</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/gamipress/\" title=\"GamiPress\" rel=\"ugc\">Get the GamiPress plugin</a>.</p>\n<p>This plugin was originally developed for the <a href=\"https://www.giz.de/akademie/en/html/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Academy of International Cooperation</a> of <a href=\"https://www.giz.de\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">GIZ</a>.</p>\n<h4>Contact</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://konnektiv.de/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Konnektiv</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload, activate and configure the free <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/gamipress/\" title=\"GamiPress\" rel=\"ugc\">GamiPress plugin</a> to WordPress.</li>\n<li>Upload &#8216;gamipress-award-on-click&#8217; Add-on to the &#8216;/wp-content/plugins/&#8217; directory</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.0.0 &#8211; 2020-09-14</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Prepare for packaging and distribution. First public release.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>0.0.1 &#8211; 2020-01-14</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial port from BadgeOS.</li>\n</ul>\n"
    },
